{"tid":1870774,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"冒便衣警叩門查「肺炎檢疫」　內地婦被盜1萬元現金","createTime":"2020-02-09T05:26:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-09T06:28:03.000Z","uid":39464,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"eca7d3b4fe03f770ea52650ec0b55701e37bb395","tid":1870774,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T05:26:15.000Z","msg":"一名內地婦人今（9日）凌晨於深水埗一間酒店房內，遭兩名自稱「便衣警」的男子闖入，被盜去1萬元現金，是4個月內第3宗假冒警員騙案。<br />\n<br />\n29歲姓黃內地婦人入住深水埗大南街156至158號一間酒店，今日凌晨約2時，兩名自稱「便衣警」的男子叩門搜查，訛稱「跟進武漢肺炎強制檢疫情況」而進入房間，逗留短時間後離去。事隔1小時後，女事主發現手袋內約1萬元現金被盜走，致電友人商討後決定報警。<br />\n<br />\n警方到場調查，將案件列作盜竊及冒充警務人員，交由深水埗警區刑事調查隊第2隊跟進，正追緝兩名身高約1.7米，案發時戴口罩及分別身穿灰色及黑色上衣的男子。<br />\n<br />\n今次是4個月內第3宗假冒警員騙案。元旦日傍晚，63歲黃姓男子途經屯門警署附近時，遭兩名自稱「便衣警」男子截查身分證，其中一人身材健壯，地點又鄰近屯門警署，黃男不虞有詐，豈料兩人趁機搶去黃男手上一個裝有21萬元現金的紙袋逃去。<br />\n<br />\n去年10月25日凌晨，一名男子在沙田麗豪酒店向29歲內地女住客自稱是「警務人員」，要求檢查事主財物，事主按指示讓男子檢查，其後發現約3萬元現金及一隻價值約1.3萬元的手鐲不翼而飛。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200209/s00001/1581211419498/%e5%86%92%e4%be%bf%e8%a1%a3%e8%ad%a6%e5%8f%a9%e9%96%80%e6%9f%a5%e3%80%8c%e8%82%ba%e7%82%8e%e6%aa%a2%e7%96%ab%e3%80%8d-%e5%85%a7%e5%9c%b0%e5%a9%a6%e8%a2%ab%e7%9b%9c1%e8%90%ac%e5%85%83%e7%8f%be%e9%87%91\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200209%2Fs00001%2F1581211419498%2F%25e5%2586%2592%25e4%25be%25bf%25e8%25a1%25a3%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e5%258f%25a9%25e9%2596%2580%25e6%259f%25a5%25e3%2580%258c%25e8%2582%25ba%25e7%2582%258e%25e6%25aa%25a2%25e7%2596%25ab%25e3%2580%258d-%25e5%2585%25a7%25e5%259c%25b0%25e5%25a9%25a6%25e8%25a2%25ab%25e7%259b%259c1%25e8%2590%25ac%25e5%2585%2583%25e7%258f%25be%25e9%2587%2591&d=CEXeqV9R6719hdRRqmVjOqDCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=a3f73324\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200209%2Fs00001%2F1581211419498%2F%25e5%2586%2592%25e4%25be%25bf%25e8%25a1%25a3%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e5%258f%25a9%25e9%2596%2580%25e6%259f%25a5%25e3%2580%258c%25e8%2582%25ba%25e7%2582%258e%25e6%25aa%25a2%25e7%2596%25ab%25e3%2580%258d-%25e5%2585%25a7%25e5%259c%25b0%25e5%25a9%25a6%25e8%25a2%25ab%25e7%259b%259c1%25e8%2590%25ac%25e5%2585%2583%25e7%258f%25be%25e9%2587%2591&h=44174dc2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200209/s00001/1581211419498/%e5%86%92%e4%be%bf%e8%a1%a3%e8%ad%a6%e5%8f%a9%e9%96%80%e6%9f%a5%e3%80%8c%e8%82%ba%e7%82%8e%e6%aa%a2%e7%96%ab%e3%80%8d-%e5%85%a7%e5%9c%b0%e5%a9%a6%e8%a2%ab%e7%9b%9c1%e8%90%ac%e5%85%83%e7%8f%be%e9%87%91</a>"},{"pid":"057abef1022dbbf776fb689c661c4161d112624d","tid":1870774,"uid":15605,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T05:27:21.000Z","msg":"唔一定係冒"},{"pid":"7d86207a2238f741b324b42babe7049da85defc7","tid":1870774,"uid":24641,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T05:27:53.000Z","msg":"想問下點樣分係咪假冒"},{"pid":"39bf0ff0c1c54a6b368ca8dbc14602a8509ac752","tid":1870774,"uid":331551,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T05:33:17.000Z","msg":"而家香港有真的嗎?!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da6f9b685a55eecb5180de2827d2ecbe49ab10a0","tid":1870774,"uid":165749,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T05:35:08.000Z","msg":"多謝黑警啦"},{"pid":"23c4ec0ed6855cadd4854a3244f61a0f937f47b9","tid":1870774,"uid":35507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T05:37:08.000Z","msg":"支那雞"},{"pid":"7dbbb78275d9fd980e210efa6d1d20988b02cf2e","tid":1870774,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T05:38:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a5eccbd82a61ac744aa33e7dddaac2bf6a89d13","tid":1870774,"uid":38030,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T05:39:31.000Z","msg":"黑警連冒警罪都犯埋，世界上已經冇嘢可以阻到黑警犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces